              "originalPosition": 142,
              "body": "````suggestion\nFigure 3 shows a one-to-one mapping case between the owner and the proxy. In this case, the function of owner can be integrated directly into the proxy, collapsing the hierarchy into a single entity to simplify the deployment. Moreover, this model also supports a one-to-many topology, allowing a central owner to manage multiple proxies across various trust domains.\n````",
